    <item>
      <title>英国批准建设两座大型太阳能发电场以扩大发电容量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/uk-approves-two-major-solar-farms-in-drive-to-grow-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源大臣埃德·米利班德批准了两个大型太阳能项目，政府希望借此推动投资并减少电力系统的二氧化碳排放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/uk-approves-two-major-solar-farms-in-drive-to-grow-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京称已准备好与特朗普讨论石油和能源问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/putin-says-he-s-ready-to-discuss-oil-energy-issues-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京表示，他准备与美国领导人唐纳德·特朗普进行面对面会谈，讨论原油价格和其他能源问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/putin-says-he-s-ready-to-discuss-oil-energy-issues-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
